items.sentence: I think it\'s time for me to get my own place.
Both my mom and my dad aren\'t home right now.
I have already told Tom that Mary isn\'t here.
Tom used to be drunk by this time every night.
Tom walked in the door at just the right time.
Tom wanted Mary to help him with his homework.
You don\'t need a sledgehammer to crack a nut.
You don\'t need to tell Tom. He already knows.
You don\'t really want me to kiss you, do you?
Tom told me that he\'d never done that before.
